  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Post-apocalyptic RPG in an open world sandbox.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚙︎ <strong>Full crafting</strong> — technology, turrets, weapons, bases, robots, tools, and landscape alteration.<br>🚗 <strong>50+ vehicles</strong> — cars, jetpacks, ships, platforms, teleports.<br>🌍 <strong>Open world</strong> — islands, infected zones, underwater territories (in development).<br>🧬 <strong>RPG system</strong> — levels, skills, achievements, full character customization.<br>⚔ <strong>Combat</strong> — mutants, mercenaries, hand-to-hand combat, shooting.<br>🏗 <strong>Base building</strong> — shelters, garages, farms, generators, defense systems, and minefields.<br>💀 <strong>Survival</strong> — hunger, thirst, sleep, stamina, infection.<br>🧍 <strong>60+ NPCs</strong> — dialogues, quests, traders.<br>🎮 <strong>Cinematic graphics</strong> — style and atmosphere settings.<br>🔄 <strong>Regular updates</strong> — new content, story events, mechanic improvements, and additions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539280/extras/6d0bea83c3f3fff40a1f8c2e5e69a942.avif?t=1772673095\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539280/extras_big/6d0bea83c3f3fff40a1f8c2e5e69a942.avif?t=1772673095 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539280/extras/3974783e9a711669505047876a97e021.avif?t=1772673095\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539280/extras_big/3974783e9a711669505047876a97e021.avif?t=1772673095 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539280/extras/b1043d8cdd54a8327302a2bb0b497e88.avif?t=1772673095\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539280/extras_big/b1043d8cdd54a8327302a2bb0b497e88.avif?t=1772673095 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539280/extras/a88e0c3db9308c553f28ad9fc6fd75f1.avif?t=1772673095\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539280/extras_big/a88e0c3db9308c553f28ad9fc6fd75f1.avif?t=1772673095 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Post-apocalyptic RPG in an open world sandbox.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚙︎ <strong>Full crafting</strong> — technology, turrets, weapons, bases, robots, tools, and landscape alteration.<br>🚗 <strong>50+ vehicles</strong> — cars, jetpacks, ships, platforms, teleports.<br>🌍 <strong>Open world</strong> — islands, infected zones, underwater territories (in development).<br>🧬 <strong>RPG system</strong> — levels, skills, achievements, full character customization.<br>⚔ <strong>Combat</strong> — mutants, mercenaries, hand-to-hand combat, shooting.<br>🏗 <strong>Base building</strong> — shelters, garages, farms, generators, defense systems, and minefields.<br>💀 <strong>Survival</strong> — hunger, thirst, sleep, stamina, infection.<br>🧍 <strong>60+ NPCs</strong> — dialogues, quests, traders.<br>🎮 <strong>Cinematic graphics</strong> — style and atmosphere settings.<br>🔄 <strong>Regular updates</strong> — new content, story events, mechanic improvements, and additions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539280/extras/6d0bea83c3f3fff40a1f8c2e5e69a942.avif?t=1772673095\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539280/extras_big/6d0bea83c3f3fff40a1f8c2e5e69a942.avif?t=1772673095 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539280/extras/3974783e9a711669505047876a97e021.avif?t=1772673095\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539280/extras_big/3974783e9a711669505047876a97e021.avif?t=1772673095 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539280/extras/b1043d8cdd